      "message": "JFYI, no action required: Idiomatic way to provide debug pretty printer functions is to implement fmt.Stringer or fmt.GoStringer. Then you can pretty-print an object easily with %v / %#v.\n\nhttps://godoc.org/fmt#Stringer\nhttps://godoc.org/fmt#GoStringer\n\nHowever in this case we want to pretty-print with indent parameter, so this way looks okay to me.",
