      "message": "nit: Here we want to do:\n\n1. Gather a list of default config files\n2. Call ResolveHostFromFiles\n\nSo I recommend writing code in this way, e.g.\n\n var paths []string\n if homeDir, err :\u003d os.UserHomeDir(); err \u003d\u003d nil {\n   paths \u003d append(paths, ...)\n }\n paths \u003d append(paths, ...)\n return ResolveHostFromFiles(addr, paths)",
